### Checkout (Requires Auth Token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "shippingAddress": "123 Saree St, Colombo, Sri Lanka"
}

###

### Webhook Simulation (Simulate PayHere success)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments/notify
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

merchant_id=test_merchant_id&order_id=1&payhere_amount=1500.00&payhere_currency=LKR&status_code=2&md5sig=MOCK_MD5_SIGNATURE
